content: Played this a lot as a kid on my pc. Now that it's on my phone, I play it everywhere.
Bought this game because I loved playing it as a kid but every time you try and use it it shuts down would give it a -1 rate if I could
Hey guys, they fixed the backgrounds! 5 stars now.
the town part with the scrolling background is govered in green dots. Had to stop playing it because I feel insulted.

At least this one gets past the licensing page, but the graphics/background is so grainy that I can't even see! Humungous is doing terrible with their Freddi Fish games. Waste of money for apps that don't work.
Pretty good other than the green background

The graphics are HORRIBLE. all good up until it comes to exploring the 
town. Anytime I go into a place it's perfect, but when I come back out, 
it's all green and discolored. But all the characters are colored just 
fine. I paid 5$ for something I can barely see?

The g ame was just as good as I remember however like many others here have said, there are major issues with the background as it is a grainy green. Please fix this graphics issue and I will rate this 5 stars
Great, just as i remember it but the background is green and fuzzy as mentioned heaps of times by other people, would appreciate either a fix or a refund thanks
One of my favorites games as child but the background  is fuzzy and green needs to be fixed thanks if fixed i will give 5 stars
It looks easy but it is really changelling
I hav waited for you guys to fix the background.  Iwould love to enjoy this game again.
Really enjoyed this game as a child would appreciate it if you guys would fix the back screen would give it 5 stars if you can fix it

The game is fun to play, but there is a major background issue. When Freddie and Luther have to get permission from the mayor to investigate coral park the background turns green and fuzzy. Seems like there's an issue there. Please fix this.
The screen is messed up & i wld really like for u guys to fix it, plz.
